Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:11.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Nice! You’ve really gotten the steps down, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If you keep this up, tomorrow’s performance will go great!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:19.40,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ehehe, really!? Yay!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:26.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Well, I am a little worried about running out of battery up there, but I’m sure I’ll manage!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m a school idol now, after all!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:34.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then we’ll stand just offstage and send you our energy!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:37.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Just… like this!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Do it with me, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:41.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh!? U-Uh, okay!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:44.62,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Rurino-chan…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:48.96,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Good luck, good luck…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:53.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I pray you’ll finish strong…!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha, thanks, you two! {\i1}Thank you{\i0}!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.56,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan, come with me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:14.61,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You really shocked Kaho-chan and Sayaka-chan there, y’know?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.37,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I mean, you just came over with this scary look on your face.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:21.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I wonder how I’ll explain this to them later~.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:22.82,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What’s the meaning of this?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.12,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Why did you put my name on this?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You didn’t even–\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:31.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megu-chan, why don’t you go out there with me?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s perform together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.85,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…This isn’t a joke.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.18,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I can’t dance anymore because of my injury.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:42.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,This is just…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.52,Megumi,,0,0,0,,this is just rude, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:47.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re coming with me…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:53.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve already decided, you’re going out there and performing with me!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:54.85,Megumi,,0,0,0,,For the last time, I–!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.34,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re coming! I’m not taking no for an answer!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.61,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’ll be out there with me! We’re doing this together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:05.57,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It’s not that simple, you know!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:07.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re coming!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Didn’t… Didn’t you want to perform too?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:17.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then let’s just do it! Together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.38,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I… I’ve…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.53,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ve already given up on it.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.53,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That still hasn’t changed…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:31.67,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m worried that this might not go well, too, but…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:37.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But as long as I’m with you, I’m sure I can do this!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So please, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll be waiting!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:46.94,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah… Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:56.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s been so long!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it has.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,How’ve you been since you transferred?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.87,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Made any new friends?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…N-Not really…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re not here, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:14.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Alright, looks like you need a present from good old Megu-chan then!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you home right now?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.62,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Could ya turn your TV on?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Okay…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.94,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah! You’re on TV, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Wow! That’s so amazing! How did this happen!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.63,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Stuff like this is easy when I get serious~!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Wow~\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.36,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s enough moping around, got it?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:45.53,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:49.12,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ll always be somewhere where you can see me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.91,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ll keep you focused on me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:56.58,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So I want you to smile, okay?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.80,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Um, actually, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I… I wanted to give you a present too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:06.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.96,Megumi,,0,0,0,,These shoes are super cute!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m really happy you like them!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:28.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Your dancing was always super cool, so I figured…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:32.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’d probably want ones that are easy to move around in.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hey, so, Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.88,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been slowly making more and more friends too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been trying really hard.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That way, one day, I’ll be able to send smiles to you too, Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.42,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hm, hm…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But I’m getting further and further ahead, you know?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:56.79,Megumi,,0,0,0,,As long as I’ve got these shoes from you, I feel like I can run to the ends of the earth!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-Well…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then, I’ll just have to go hard, too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:09.18,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll go abroad and get big! Then I can take a plane to catch up to you real quick!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.34,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And then we can have fun together again!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.27,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s have fun together again, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll definitely catch up to you!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:23.58,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:24.90,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ll be waiting!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:32.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Those words.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:33.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No, never mind.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.20,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But, I understand now.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.42,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The reason I became a school idol was…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.30,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Because I had so much fun with you.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:51.17,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Experiencing new things together, and seeing everyone around us having so much fun…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:55.74,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It made me want to captivate them all more and more.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s why I’ve been running this long…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.47,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ruri-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.69,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But you’re too late…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.79,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-Why…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I just got back!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:17.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’ll be okay! You were always able to do anything, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not even an injury could keep you down for long–\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No, you’re wrong!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ve been pretending this whole time!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:30.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,All I was doing was trying to look good for you!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I would secretly practice dancing all the time!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:39.23,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I failed so many child acting auditions over and over again!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:40.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was for you to be happy…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.55,Megumi,,0,0,0,,for you to keep smiling…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.96,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I should’ve told you about my injury much earlier!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:07:01.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That way, you wouldn’t have felt like you needed to enroll here.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ve been running away…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.86,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Because I didn’t want you to see this side of me…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.76,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Th-that’s…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.69,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You understand now, right, Ruri-chan?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:27.00,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Fujishima Megumi has never been the cool girl you looked up to.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.00,Megumi,,0,0,0,,She’s nothing but a loser and a coward…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:35.18,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And even now, she’s still terrified of returning to the stage.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:41.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry for lying to you all this time.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.80,Rurino,,0,0,0,,M-Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:48.97,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ll always support your school idol activities, okay?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So… Please take care of the club for me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.84,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
